  "content": "<p></p><h1 class=\"title\">Green Faith</h1><h2><b>The Old Faith</b></h2><b>Source</b> <a class=\"external-link\" href=\"http://paizo.com/products/btpy91dm?Pathfinder-Adventure-Path-75-Demons-Heresy\" target=\"_blank\"><i>Pathfinder #75: Demon's Heresy pg. 64</i></a><br /><b>Pathfinder Wiki</b> <a href=\"http://www.pathfinderwiki.com/wiki/Green Faith\">Green Faith</a><p></p><h3 class=\"framing\">Details</h3><p><b>Alignment</b> N<br /><b>Pantheon</b> Core Deities<br /><b>Areas of Concern</b> Air, beast, earth, fire, water<br /><b>Domains</b> <a href=\"DomainDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Air\">Air</a>, <a href=\"DomainDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Animal\">Animal</a>, <a href=\"DomainDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Earth\">Earth</a>, <a href=\"DomainDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Fire\">Fire</a>, <a href=\"DomainDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Plant\">Plant</a><br /><b>Subdomains</b> <a href=\"DomainDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Plant\">Leshy</a><br /><i>* Requires the <u><a href=\"TraitDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Acolyte%20of%20Apocrypha\">Acolyte of Apocrypha</a></u> trait.</i><br /><b>Favored Weapon</b> Druidic weapons<br /></p><h2 class=\"title\">For Followers of Green Faith</h2><p></p><h3 class=\"framing\">Archetypes</h3><p><a href=\"ArchetypeDisplay.aspx?FixedName=Bard Cultivator\">Cultivator (Bard)</a>, <a href=\"ArchetypeDisplay.aspx?FixedName=Druid Green Faith Initiate\">Green Faith Initiate (Druid)</a>, <a href=\"ArchetypeDisplay.aspx?FixedName=Inquisitor Green Faith Marshal\">Green Faith Marshal (Inquisitor)</a></p><h3 class=\"framing\">Feats</h3><p><a href=\"FeatDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Green Faith Acolyte\">Green Faith Acolyte</a></p><h3 class=\"framing\">Magic Items - Weapons</h3><p><a href=\"MagicWeaponsDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Midsummer Sickle\">Midsummer Sickle</a></p><h3 class=\"framing\">Magic Items - Wondrous Items</h3><p><a href=\"MagicWondrousDisplay.aspx?FinalName=Evergreen Seed Pouch\">Evergreen Seed Pouch</a>, <a href=\"MagicWondrousDisplay.aspx?FinalName=Warden's Cudgel\">Warden's Cudgel</a></p><h3 class=\"framing\">Prestige Classes</h3><p><a href=\"PrestigeClassesDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Green Faith Acolyte\">Green Faith Acolyte</a></p><h3 class=\"framing\">Spells</h3><p><a href=\"SpellDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Hibernate\">Hibernate</a>, <a href=\"SpellDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Summon Elemental Steed\">Summon Elemental Steed</a>, <a href=\"SpellDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Tripvine\">Tripvine</a></p><h3 class=\"framing\">Traits</h3><p><a href=\"TraitDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Eyes of the Wild\">Eyes of the Wild</a>, <a href=\"TraitDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Know the Land\">Know the Land</a></p><h2 class=\"title\">Unique Summon Rules</h2><b>Source </b><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"http://paizo.com/products/btpy91dm?Pathfinder-Adventure-Path-75-Demons-Heresy\" target=\"_blank\"><i>Pathfinder #75: Demon's Heresy pg. 64</i></a><br /><a href=\"SpellDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Summon Nature's Ally 2\"><b>Summon Nature's Ally II</b></a>: <a href=\"MonsterDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Axe Beak\">Axe Beak</a> [Order of Wing]<br /><a href=\"SpellDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Summon Nature's Ally 2\"><b>Summon Nature's Ally II</b></a>: <a href=\"MonsterDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Dire Badger\">Dire Badger</a> [Order of Earth]<br /><a href=\"SpellDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Summon Nature's Ally 2\"><b>Summon Nature's Ally II</b></a>: <a href=\"MonsterDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Giant Porcupine\">Giant Porcupine</a> [Order of Earth]<br /><a href=\"SpellDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Summon Nature's Ally 4\"><b>Summon Nature's Ally IV</b></a>: <a href=\"MonsterDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Giant Chameleon\">Giant Chameleon Lizard</a> [Order of Fang]<br /><a href=\"SpellDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Summon Nature's Ally 4\"><b>Summon Nature's Ally IV</b></a>: <a href=\"MonsterDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Giant Skunk\">Giant Skunk</a> [Order of Earth]<br /><a href=\"SpellDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Summon Nature's Ally 4\"><b>Summon Nature's Ally IV</b></a>: <a href=\"MonsterDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Seaweed Leshy\">Seaweed Leshy</a> [Order of Leaf or Wave]<br /><a href=\"SpellDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Summon Nature's Ally 4\"><b>Summon Nature's Ally IV</b></a>: <a href=\"MonsterDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Giant Vulture\">Giant Vulture</a> [Order of Wing]<br /><a href=\"SpellDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Summon Nature's Ally 5\"><b>Summon Nature's Ally V</b></a>: <a href=\"MonsterDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Emperor Cobra\">Emperor Cobra</a> [Order of Fang]<br /><a href=\"SpellDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Summon Nature's Ally 5\"><b>Summon Nature's Ally V</b></a>: <a href=\"MonsterDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Great Horned Owl\">Giant Owl</a> [Order of Wing]<br /><a href=\"SpellDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Summon Nature's Ally 5\"><b>Summon Nature's Ally V</b></a>: <a href=\"MonsterDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Giant Gar\">Giant Gar</a> [Order of Wave]<br /><a href=\"SpellDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Summon Nature's Ally 6\"><b>Summon Nature's Ally VI</b></a>: <a href=\"MonsterDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Shambling Mound\">Shambling Mound</a> [Order of Leaf]<br /><a href=\"SpellDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Summon Nature's Ally 7\"><b>Summon Nature's Ally VII</b></a>: <a href=\"MonsterDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Giant Snapping Turtle\">Giant Snapping Turtle</a> [Order of Wave]<br /><a href=\"SpellDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Summon Nature's Ally 7\"><b>Summon Nature's Ally VII</b></a>: <a href=\"MonsterDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Giant Anaconda\">Giant Anaconda</a> [Order of Fang]<br /><a href=\"SpellDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Summon Nature's Ally 7\"><b>Summon Nature's Ally VII</b></a>: <a href=\"MonsterDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Giant Flytrap\">Giant Flytrap</a> [Order of Leaf]<br /><h2 class=\"title\">Other Rules</h2><b>Source </b><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"http://paizo.com/products/btpy91dm?Pathfinder-Adventure-Path-75-Demons-Heresy\" target=\"_blank\"><i>Pathfinder #75: Demon's Heresy pg. 64</i></a><br />No clerics of the Green Faith, domains are for Druids. The Green Faith is not headed by a deity, but is an order that worships and gains power from nature.<br /><br /><p></p><div style=\"position:relative;left:0%;border:2px ridge #434343;width:100%;height:100%\"><div class=\"wiki-content-full\"><iframe style=\"overflow-y:hidden;width:100%;height:450px\" src=\"https://pathfinderwiki.com/wiki/Green Faith\"> </iframe></div>\n </div>",
